<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q37_v6" title="Q37_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceD</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Se muestra la resolución de un estudiante para la siguiente ecuación lineal:</p>
    <p>
      Paso 1:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math><br />
      Paso 2:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math><br />
      Paso 3:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math><br />
      Paso 4:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
    </p>
    <p>¿En cuál de los pasos el estudiante comete el primer error?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Selecciona una alternativa.</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">En el Paso 1<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El Paso 1 solo presenta la ecuación inicial <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y no hay transformación que revisar todavía. El primer paso incorrecto aparece después.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">En el Paso 2<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Pasar de <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> es correcto, porque se suma <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> en ambos lados. Así se obtiene una ecuación equivalente.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">En el Paso 3<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Simplificar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo tanto <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> es correcto. El primer error todavía no aparece en ese paso.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">En el Paso 4<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Desde <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> no se debe escribir <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Para despejar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> hay que dividir ambos lados por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Revisión paso a paso de la resolución</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Ecuación inicial</strong></p>
            <p>La ecuación dada es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Aquí no hay error, porque solo se escribe la ecuación original.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Sumar 4 en ambos lados</strong></p>
            <p>Para eliminar el <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, se suma <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> a ambos lados:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces queda <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Este paso es correcto.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Simplificar el lado derecho</strong></p>
            <p>Se calcula <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la ecuación queda <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Este paso también es correcto.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Despejar la variable</strong></p>
            <p>Desde <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, para despejar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> hay que dividir ambos lados por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>28</m:mn><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>28</m:mn><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>El estudiante, en cambio, escribió <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, que no corresponde a dividir por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Aquí aparece el primer error.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El primer error está en el Paso 4, por lo tanto la alternativa correcta es la D.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>